      "content": "thanks for these. they're actually really helpful for the structure. i also need to cover the cultural side of it. some people at the time argued that segregation was actually better for \"cultural preservation\" to prevent different groups from losing their identity. can you expand on how they would frame that as a positive or necessary thing for social stability?",
